Inez Bensusan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inez_Bensusan 0 Inez Bensusan (1871–1967) was an Australian born Jewish actor, playwright and suffragette in the UK. She was a leader of the Actresses' Franchise League and the Jewish League for Woman Suffrage.
